OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FApprentices quit over poor 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fquality schemes, report    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands of people are dropping out of
OL,6, apprenticeships every year, after firms
OL,7, provided little or no training,        
OL,8, according to a report.                 
OL,10,FThe most recent official data suggests 
OL,11,Fthat nearly half of apprentices fail to
OL,12,Fcomplete their courses.                
OL,14,FEDSK, a think tank, found that the     
OL,15,Fmajority of people quitting cited "poor
OL,16,Fquality", including lack of training   
OL,17,Fand bad management.                    
OL,19,FThe government said it is introducing  
OL,20,Freforms "to boost quality".            
